      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600">
        <p class="mb-6">
          Man and van combines a professional driver with a suitable vehicle for moving your items. Unlike full removal services, you may help with loading (though many operators offer full loading assistance), and you typically handle your own packing beforehand. It's the middle ground between hiring a van yourself and booking a complete removal team.
        </p>
        <p>
          The service suits people who need more than their own car can carry but don't have enough belongings to justify a full house removal. You get experience and proper equipment at a fraction of the cost, with the flexibility to book by the hour.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

