        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üì¶</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">eBay & Marketplace</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Collecting purchases from sellers when items are too large for your own vehicle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üíº</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Office Items</h3>
