            Blankets
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="text-xl block mb-1">üìê</span>
            Ramps
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Man and Van Pricing</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600">
        <p class="mb-6">
          Man and van services typically charge by the hour, making them cost-effective for smaller, quicker jobs. Here's what affects the price:
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Pricing Factors</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li><strong>Time:</strong> Hourly rate √ó hours needed</li>
              <li><strong>Van size:</strong> Larger vans cost more</li>
              <li><strong>Helpers:</strong> Extra pair of hands available</li>
              <li><strong>Distance:</strong> Longer journeys may affect rates</li>
              <li><strong>Access:</strong> Stairs or difficult parking</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Typical Minimums</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li><strong>Minimum booking:</strong> Usually 1-2 hours</li>
              <li><strong>Small van:</strong> Suits boxes and small items</li>
              <li><strong>Medium van:</strong> Most popular for moves</li>
              <li><strong>Large van:</strong> For bigger jobs</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>
          Getting a few quotes helps you compare options and find the best value for your particular move. Be specific about what you're moving and any access challenges to get accurate estimates.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Man and Van vs Full Removal -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Man and Van vs Full Removal Service</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b">
              <th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold">Feature</th>
              <th class="text-center p-4 font-semibold">Man and Van</th>
              <th class="text-center p-4 font-semibold">Full Removal</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-sm">
            <tr class="border-b">
              <td class="p-4">Best for</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">Small moves, single items</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">Full house moves</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b">
              <td class="p-4">Pricing</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">Hourly</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">Fixed quote</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b">
              <td class="p-4">Packing</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">You pack</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">Optional service</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b">
              <td class="p-4">Loading help</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">Varies by operator</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">Fully managed</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b">
              <td class="p-4">Team size</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">1-2 people</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">2-4+ people</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-4">Cost</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center text-green-600 font-medium">Lower</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center">Higher</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mt-6">
        Not sure which you need? Contact us and we'll recommend the best option for your situation.
      </p>
